release.notes:
Second label with "SW".  First labels had "SO".  Runouts have corrected "SO" to "SW".

"Mfd by Apple Records Inc" rim text on Side B.

"APPLE SW-385" on spine and back cover

Title is "Hey Jude" on the spine and "The Beatles Again" on the labels

Side A label has "Can't buy me Love" title and songwriter credit appearing above the spindle hole
B4 is printed as "Ballad Of John & Yoko" on the label, and "Ballad Of John And Yoko" on the back cover
"Printed in USA" in a small circle on the bottom right of the back cover
